	    <sgmltag>bookinfo</sgmltag> elemek
	    seg&iacute;ts&eacute;g&eacute;vel defini&aacute;lt
	    k&ouml;nyvsablon</title>

	  <programlisting>&lt;book>
  &lt;bookinfo>
    &lt;title><replaceable>Ide &iacute;rjuk a c&iacute;met</replaceable>&lt;/title>

